Description: It is a system assistant tool developed by UbuntuKylin Team.
 Helps all users manage their linux system conveniently. 
 In this 0.1 Release, it provides three features: 
 show system information, customize the system UI,
 and clean the system garbage. More features are 
 developing for its future release.
